---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me" description="Learn more about the author of this blog">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Me</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p>
        Hello! I'm a passionate developer and writer who loves to share knowledge and experiences through this blog.
        I focus on web development, programming best practices, and emerging technologies.
      </p>
      
      <h2>My Background</h2>
      <p>
        I have several years of experience in software development, specializing in front-end technologies like React, 
        Vue, and Angular. I also have experience with back-end development using Node.js, Python, and various databases.
      </p>
      
      <h2>What I Write About</h2>
      <p>
        On this blog, you'll find articles about:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Web development tutorials and best practices</li>
        <li>Programming tips and tricks</li>
        <li>New technology reviews and explorations</li>
        <li>My personal projects and learnings</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>My Skills</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Frontend</h3>
          <ul class="mt-2">
            <li>React</li>
            <li>Vue</li>
            <li>Angular</li>
            <li>HTML/CSS</li>
            <li>Tailwind CSS</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Backend</h3>
          <ul class="mt-2">
            <li>Node.js</li>
            <li>Express</li>
            <li>Python</li>
            <li>Django</li>
            <li>FastAPI</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Other</h3>
          <ul class="mt-2">
            <li>Git</li>
            <li>Docker</li>
            <li>AWS</li>
            <li>CI/CD</li>
            <li>Testing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2>Contact Me</h2>
      <p>
        Feel free to reach out to me through any of the following channels:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:example@example.com">example@example.com</a></li>
        <li>Twitter: <a href="https://twitter.com/example" target="_blank">@example</a></li>
        <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/example" target="_blank">github.com/example</a></li>
        <li>LinkedIn: <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/example" target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/example</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
